<img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-1786539 lazyload lazyload" src="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Mercy-Chinwo.jpeg" alt="" width="1280" height="1267" srcset="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Mercy-Chinwo.jpeg 898w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Mercy-Chinwo-604x598.jpeg 604w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Mercy-Chinwo-58x58.jpeg 58w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Mercy-Chinwo-116x116.jpeg 116w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Mercy-Chinwo-100x100.jpeg 100w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Mercy-Chinwo-242x240.jpeg 242w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Mercy-Chinwo-485x480.jpeg 485w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Mercy-Chinwo-600x594.jpeg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px" /> Gospel singer Mercy Chinwo and beau and Pastor Blessed Uzochikwa have announced their engagement. The couple took to Instagram to share photos from their engagement shoot. In her post, Mercy Chinwo wrote, “I am blessed to be blessed with @theofficialblessed The thoughts of doing the next phase and the rest phase of my life with you makes the blessing more real I love you Sweet.”   A post shared by MERCYCHINWO (@mercychinwo) Pastor Uzochikwa also shared his love, writing, “I’M THE MAN THE LORD SHOWED MERCY! @mercychinwo thanks for saying YES! I LOVE YOU DEARLY ! Ecclesiastical 9:9 Live happily with the woman you love through all the meaningless days of life that God has given you under the sun. The wife God gives you is your REWARD for all your earthly toil. #Mercyisblessed.” Mercy Chinwo is a prominent Nigerian gospel artist, singer, and composer known for producing songs like Excess Love, Omekanaya, and Obinasom. And Pastor Blessed Uzochikwa is the resident pastor of The Waterbrook (TWB) Church.